{"tid":1054799,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【女教師墮樓】校長從未接觸過家屬 老父含淚：要為個女討回公道","createTime":"2019-03-10T06:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T11:49:52.000Z","uid":72676,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"59106f59841c9d7dbe61b5a0cb335955c67ca430","tid":1054799,"uid":72676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:07:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190310/59351445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190310%2F59351445&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2Et47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=1046fb4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190310%2F59351445&h=87a5aadb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190310/59351445</a><br />\n<br />\n天水圍東華三院李東海小學女教師疑不堪工作壓力，上周三（6日）於校園內墮樓身亡。今日東華三院董事局，包括主席、校監等將到學校，出席下午的打齋超渡儀式。死者父親及胞弟早上到學校，其中死者父親失去愛女，痛心不已，矢言要替女兒討回公道。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：教協：小學工作壓力直逼中學<br />\n<br />\n林老師的父親於上午10時45分左右，由親友陪同到學校。他指事發至今，校長未有接觸過家屬，不過他自己亦不想見到對方。林父含淚說：「作為父親，梗係想為個女討回公道。」聲言會向學校追究。<br />\n<br />\n有家長今早特意帶來鮮花，放在校門石壆上鞠躬致祭。房先生的女兒讀小六，他表示不清楚事件始末，不便評論，但女兒曾向他說：「校長自己唔做嘢，想人幫佢做嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【女教師墮樓】個個都有壓力 家長：教育制度成日變<br />\n<br />\n東華三院主席王賢誌，今早已經到學校。他較早前指，將召開緊急會議並成立獨立調查委員會調查事件（ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Uv5jIG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Uv5jIG&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2Et47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=17bf7800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Uv5jIG</a> ）。<br />\n<br />\n事發於上周三早上7時23分，林老師在校園內墮樓，當場斃命。事後林的3名胞弟妹趕到學校，透露林生前曾經訴說工作壓力大，又指「校長好多無理要求」，並稱「佢（死者）一向同學校關係唔係咁好」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果就咁放過嗰校長真係無天理！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf63762cf0f03065d88933272f0829803434f581","tid":1054799,"uid":42188,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:10:09.000Z","msg":"羅校長而家根本淆撚到仆街<br />\n連出來講句野/見家屬都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56821706a42e6de17f080a6cb5d4033d984b64a","tid":1054799,"uid":126648,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"bf63762cf0f03065d88933272f0829803434f581","tid":1054799,"uid":42188,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:10:09.000Z","msg":"羅校長而家根本淆撚到仆街<br />\n連出來講句野/見家屬都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"唔係早幾日先話咩一切照常咩<br />\n潛一陣水想當冇左件事啦 香港人好快唔記得"},{"pid":"f69dee324547d6e36922ade701d03aefc725e936","tid":1054799,"uid":42188,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f56821706a42e6de17f080a6cb5d4033d984b64a","tid":1054799,"uid":126648,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"bf63762cf0f03065d88933272f0829803434f581","tid":1054799,"uid":42188,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:10:09.000Z","msg":"羅校長而家根本淆撚到仆街<br />\n連出來講句野/見家屬都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"唔係早幾日先話咩一切照常咩<br />\n潛一陣水想當冇左件事啦 香港人好快唔記得"},"citedB